---
import Heading from "../components/Heading.astro";
import Text from "../components/Text.astro";

import brandDesktop from "../assets/brandStrategy/brand-desktop.png";
import brandTablet from "../assets/brandStrategy/brand-tablet.png";
import brandMobile from "../assets/brandStrategy/brand-mobile.png";
---

<section class=`brand-section`>
  <div class="left">
    <Heading level={1} class="title">
      <span class="num">01</span> Brand <br /> Strategy
    </Heading>
  </div>

  <div class="right">
    <div class="text-block">
      <Text color="grey">
        In the world of finance, mistakes happen—miscalculations, overlooked
        expenses, inefficiencies that silently erode profitability. Businesses
        lose money not because they aren’t earning, but because errors go
        unchecked.
      </Text>

      <Text color="grey"> Redo restores confidence in financial numbers. </Text>
    </div>

    <picture>
      <source srcset={brandMobile.src} media="(max-width: 799px)" />
      <source srcset={brandTablet.src} media="(max-width: 1279px)" />
      <!-- Десктоп по умолчанию -->
      <img
        src={brandDesktop.src}
        alt="Redo Brand Strategy"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
        class="photo"
      />
    </picture>

    <div class="text-block">
      <Text color="grey">
        Born from the need for financial clarity, Redo was founded on a simple
        yet powerful mission: to correct financial errors and optimize balance
        sheets. We believe that precision is the key to profitability, and that
        businesses shouldn’t be held back by avoidable losses. With advanced
        technology and expert analysis, we uncover discrepancies, eliminate
        inefficiencies, and restore confidence in the numbers that drive
        success.
      </Text>

      <Text color="grey">
        At Redo, we don’t just fix mistakes—we empower businesses to move
        forward with accuracy and efficiency. Because when the numbers are
        right, the future looks even brighter.
      </Text>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .brand-section {
      padding: 32px 32px 128px 32px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
      background: var(--bg, #fff);
    }

    .title .num {
      color: var(--accent-2, #f45f00);
      font: inherit; /* размер/вес как у H1 */
    }

    .right {
      display: grid;
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .right .text-block {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .photo {
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1279px) and (min-width: 800px) {
      .brand-section {
        padding: 88px 20px;
      }
      .photo {
        max-width: 352px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 799px) {
      .brand-section {
        padding: 32px 20px 80px 20px;
      }
      .brand-section {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .photo {
        max-width: 335px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</section>
